get=\"#feedbackModal_main_3617046\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Apr 20, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104xti1665702633239.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/xti1665702633239.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/xti1665702633239.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"xti1665702633239\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Controls the appearance of the frame around the widget.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"xti1665702633239__topic_d104162e1_d104163e1_d104164e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xti1665702633239__p_d104165e1_d104166e1_d104167e1\">FrameType<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code><code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">3D</code> |\n               <code class=\"ph codeph\">Flat</code> | <code class=\"ph codeph\">Top</code> | <code class=\"ph codeph\">Bottom</code> |\n               <code class=\"ph codeph\">Off</code></p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section p\" id=\"xti1665702633239__section_w860ab1b5b3_w861ab1b5_w862ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xti1665702633239__p_d104168e1_d104169e1_d104170e1\">Example: <code class=\"ph codeph\">\"frametype=flat\"</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section p\" id=\"xti1665702633239__section_w863ab1b5b5_w864ab1b5_w865ab1\">\n<div class=\"p\" id=\"xti1665702633239__p_d104171e1_d104172e1_d104173e1\">\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"xti1665702633239__fig_w869ab1b5b5b1b1_w870ab1b5b5b1_w871ab1b5b5_w872ab1b5_w873ab1\">\n<br/><img alt=\"Frame type-flat\" class=\"image\" id=\"xti1665702633239__image_rlq_b24_wwb\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/frametypebuttons.png?_LANG=enus\"/><br/>\n</figure>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section table\" id=\"xti1665702633239__section_w866ab1b5b7_w867ab1b5_w868ab1\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"xti1665702633239__table_d12293e1_d12294e1_d12295e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"xti1665702633239__table_d12293e1_d12294e1_d12295e1__entry__1\">Value</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"xti1665702633239__table_d12293e1_d12294e1_d12295e1__entry__2\">Description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xti1665702633239__table_d12293e1_d12294e1_d12295e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">3D</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xti1665702633239__table_d12293e1_d12294e1_d12295e1__entry__2\">Button is displayed with a 3D frame</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xti1665702633239__table_d12293e1_d12294e1_d12295e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">Flat</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xti1665702633239__table_d12293e1_d12294e1_d12295e1__entry__2\">Button is displayed with a flat frame,\n                        consistent with Windows 8 and higher.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xti1665702633239__table_d12293e1_d12294e1_d12295e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">Top</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xti1665702633239__table_d12293e1_d12294e1_d12295e1__entry__2\">The button frame consist of a single line at\n                        the top of the button</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xti1665702633239__table_d12293e1_d12294e1_d12295e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">Bottom</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xti1665702633239__table_d12293e1_d12294e1_d12295e1__entry__2\">The button frame consist of a single line at\n                        the bottom of the button</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xti1665702633239__table_d12293e1_d12294e1_d12295e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">Off</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xti1665702633239__table_d12293e1_d12294e1_d12295e1__entry__2\">No frame is displayed around the button</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xti1665702633239__section_c1s_c24_wwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d726603e181\">Usage</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"xti1665702633239__table_d12296e1_d12297e1_d12298e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Dynamic?</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Yes</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Supported in Grid?</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">No</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Dependencies:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Representation</span> property\n                     must be set to <code class=\"ph codeph\">Uniface</code>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xti1665702633239__section_rmw_d24_wwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d726603e233\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xti1665702633239__p_d104180e1_d104181e1_d104182e1\">To set this property in the Uniface IDE, click the\n            More icon (<img alt=\"More icon\" class=\"image\" id=\"xti1665702633239__image_jcw_g24_wwb\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/ellipsis.png?_LANG=enus\"/>) in <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">&lt;CPT&gt;</var> Widget Properties</span>, then click\n               <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">More</span> in the Define Properties dialog.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xti1665702633239__section_iwt_324_wwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d726603e257\">Example: Setting in Proc</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xti1665702633239__p_d104186e1_d104187e1_d104188e1\">You can use <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$properties</span> or\n               <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$fieldproperties</span> to set or get the property and its value. For\n            more information, see the \"$properties\" and \"$fieldproperties\" topics.</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"xti1665702633239__pre_mpb_l24_wwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">operation Exec\nvariables\n string vProps\nendvariables\nputitem/id vProps, \"representation\",\"uniface\"\nputitem/id vProps, \"frametype\",\"flat\"\nputitem/id vProps, \"transparency\",\"true\"\nputitem/id vProps, \"framecolor\",\"purple\"\n$properties(BTN) = vProps\nedit\nend; exec</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xti1665702633239__section_ych_l24_wwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d726603e275\">Applies To</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"xti1665702633239__ul_ifh_m24_wwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xti1665702633239__li_d41750e1_d41751e1_d41752e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jrc1665702631553.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jrc1665702631553.html\" title=\"The CommandButton is a logical widget that enables a user to initiate an action by clicking the button.\">CommandButton</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zie1665702558978.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$properties</a><p>Return or set the current widget properties of a field.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/aud1705998763272.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$fieldproperties</a><p>Return or set the current widget properties of an instance of a field.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3617046\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3617046\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Frame Type (FrameType) Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Apr 20, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Controls the appearance of the frame around the widget. FrameType = 3D | Flat | Top | Bottom | Off Example: \"frametype=flat\" Value Description 3D Button is displayed with a 3D frame Flat Button is displayed with a flat frame, consistent with Windows 8 and higher. Top The button frame consist of a single line at the top of the button Bottom The button frame consist of a single line at the bottom of the button Off No frame is displayed around the button Usage Dynamic? Yes Supported in Grid? No Dependencies: Representation property must be set to Uniface Description To set this property in the Uniface IDE, click the More icon ( ) in <CPT> Widget Properties , then click More in the Define Properties dialog. Example: Setting in Proc You can use $properties or $fieldproperties to set or get the property and its value. For more information, see the \"$properties\" and \"$fieldproperties\" topics. operation Exec variables string vProps endvariables putitem/id vProps, \"representation\",\"uniface\" putitem/id vProps, \"frametype\",\"flat\" putitem/id vProps, \"transparency\",\"true\" putitem/id vProps, \"framecolor\",\"purple\" $properties(BTN) = vProps edit end; exec Copy Applies To CommandButton Related Links $properties Return or set the current widget properties of a field. $fieldproperties Return or set the current widget properties of an instance of a field. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}